body.name: Men's Plaque Compression Buckle Dress Belt
features: FULLY ADJUSTABLE FIT: This sleek dress belt from Dockers features a compression plaque buckle that allows you to easily glide the buckle along the belt strap until you get the perfect fit - no belt holes to hinder the fit that feels right to you. This belt ensures you're always feeling your best while elevating your outfit.
VERSATILE STYLE: This belt is perfect to pair with a variety of outfits, both dressy or casual, and the plaque style buckle gives a modern touch to your trousers, dress pants, khakis, chinos and more

MENS BELT SIZING: For best fit, order size 2 inches larger than your pant size, EX: Typically a size 36 pant, order belt size Large (38-40). Size ranges from Small through X-Large. Small (30-32), Medium (34-36), Large (38-40), X-Large (42-44)

DESIGNED BY DOCKERS: This stylish belt is built with comfort and quality in mind. Versatile enough to complete any outfit with, all Dockers belts are designed with our usual attention to detail, innovation, and timeless style that will perfectly complement your khakis, every time
body.description: An essential accessory in every man's wardrobe, this Dockers men's belt will feel secure and comfortable for all-day wear. Crafted with Custom Fit technology, Dockers custom fit belts are engineered for comfort. This belt provides endless adjustability and comfort with a modern, no-holes strap for a clean look. Designed by Dockers® with our usual attention to detail, innovation, and timeless style, Dockers belts are sure to complete you look in style.
